===Etymology===
From Seri ''[[comcaac]]'', plural of ''[[cmiique]]'' "person; Seri".
===Noun===
'''Comcáac''' ''pl.''

# The [[Seri]]s, an indigenous group of [[Sonora]], [[Mexico]].
